    <a title="Cathal Kenneally" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/31913163-cathal-kenneally"><img alt="Cathal Kenneally" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1615679543p2/31913163.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2523217033?book_show_action=true">Sep 08, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Cathal Kenneally" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Cathal Kenneally" href="/user/show/31913163-cathal-kenneally">Cathal Kenneally</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780751541427" href="/book/show/7601302-the-swan-thieves">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2523217033" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14803975736228817861">I read The Historian by the same author and enjoyed it. Unfortunately this book didn&apos;t live up to expectations. When you enjoy a book by one author you have high hopes for their next book. In the case , it wasn&apos;t to be</span>
  <span id="freeText14803975736228817861" style="display:none">I read The Historian by the same author and enjoyed it. Unfortunately this book didn't live up to expectations. When you enjoy a book by one author you have high hopes for their next book. In the case , it wasn't to be</span>
  <a data-text-id="14803975736228817861" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


